@startuml
title Viaverse AI Session / Support Ticket — State Diagram

[*] --> AI_SESSION_STARTED
AI_SESSION_STARTED --> CONTEXT_READY : build context
CONTEXT_READY --> GENERATING : safe
GENERATING --> ANSWERED : safe/confident
GENERATING --> FALLBACK : unsafe/low confidence
GENERATING --> ESCALATED_TO_SUPPORT : risky intent
FALLBACK --> ESCALATED_TO_SUPPORT : handoff
ESCALATED_TO_SUPPORT --> TICKET_OPENED : create
TICKET_OPENED --> AGENT_ASSIGNED : assign
AGENT_ASSIGNED --> RESOLVED : agent resolves
ANSWERED --> FEEDBACK_RECEIVED : user feedback
RESOLVED --> FEEDBACK_RECEIVED : support feedback

FEEDBACK_RECEIVED --> [*]

note bottom
AI answered does not mean action completed.
It means guidance was delivered.
Risky/business actions require separate confirmed domain workflow.
end note
@enduml
